<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF207-865-338  </DOCNO><DOCID>07 865 338.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>MacWEEK  Oct 24 1989 v3 n38 p3(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT MacWEEK Inc. 1989.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Animated actors come to life: InterFACE images in 8-bit color,gray scale. (Bright Star Technology develops animation program)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Guglielmo, Connie.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   Bright Star Technology Inc. (product development).andO;Product:   InterFace (Computer graphics software) (product development).andO;Topic:     Product DevelopmentAnimationGraphics SoftwareUtility Programs.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>InterFACE images in 8-bit color, gray scaleandM;By Connie GuglielmoandM;Bellevue, Wash.andP;  -- Bright Star Technology is expected to introduce nextmonth a new animation program that brings colorful, animated characters tolife on the Macintosh.andM;InterFACE, short for Interactive Facial Animation Construction Environment,builds on the capabilities of Bright Star's Hyper-Animator, a program thatlets Macintosh users create lip-synched talking actors, or &quot;agents,&quot; usingdigitized sound.andM;But unlike the monochrome HyperAnimator, interFACE supports eight-bit colorand gray-scale images.andP;  Characters can be created using the program's colorpaint tools or scanned in and edited.andP;  The $499.95 program also contains acollection of facial-feature clip art -- eyes, noses, mouths and other facialfeatures that can be cut and pasted.andM;While HyperAnimator lets users create agents with a total of 16 differentfacial expressions, interFACE supports 120 images per agent, which results inagents with a more-realistic appearance.andP;  The program also allows any numberof agents of any size on screen at the same time.andP;  It offers an improvedutility for sychronizing and compressing digitized sound as well.andM;In addition, the company is offering a $500 drive installer to developersthat allows them to distribute interFACE-generated agents.andM;Bright Star Technology is located at 1003 111th Ave. N.E., Bellevue, Wash.andO;98004; (206) 451-3697.andO;</TEXT></DOC>